gg menu\nImport v1: imports a config file with optional messages\nExport v1 :exports a config file with optional messages\nImport v2.1: imports a config file with optional messages\nExport v2.1: exports a config file with optional messages\nDelete: deletes a file\nSaveVol: saves the current volume\nOpen link: opens a link\nUpdateCheck : checks for an update with an optional ui","m_descriptionOpen":false,"m_enabled":true,"m_excludeLog":false,"m_headingColor":-16755713,"m_isOrCondition":false,"m_name":"[Bdnd api] Better don\u0027t disturb full API 4.1","m_triggerList":[{"disableLogging":false,"m_SIGUID":-5489099475822651169,"m_classType":"EmptyTrigger","m_constraintList":[],"m_isDisabled":false,"m_isOrCondition":false}]},"macroExportVersion":1}
